snippet.title: Rogue Voltage - Alpha Teaser
snippet.description:
Roguelike Deckbuilder × Modular Synthesizer

Build a rack of specialized modules. Wire them up to construct your combat actions. Generate and manage energy, manipulate the timeline, beat procedural threats and try to get the power back on in a world haunted by a permanent storm.

WISHLIST on Steam: https://s.team/a/1494560
Follow development on Twitter: https://twitter.com/_RogueVoltage
Come chat: https://discord.gg/bGpnfJFUPj
#roguelike #rpg #modularsynth #indiegame #gaming #trailer
